title: Haizuka, poster for the Haizuka Printing House. Fifth in the series. (combining elements from all four  posters in the series)

description: Poster with text: "HAIZUKA" in large black letters at angle from lower-left corner to upper-right corner. Reclining figure from Titian lower right corner, Naked Man and Woman from Dore hovering at center with images of feet on either side. Background of trains of Angels.
